title: Beautiful City of Lakes  Top Floor Studio ! @ 2876 Humboldt So.
posting_body: ['This is a very nice Top floor studio located at 2876 Humboldt Ave.', 'South Available September 1st  , You will not be able to beat the character of this apartment for the price.', 'This hardwood studio features natural woodwork walk in closet with built in storage, Heat,Water and cooking gas are included in rent.', 'You pay electricity ,You also have a full kitchen with full size gas stove and AMPLE kitchen cupboard space.', 'There is also a built-in dining room table, or maybe a desk...', 'The current resident has a bed and a couch in the main living area.', 'The kitchen and dining area are separate from the living area.', '       This is a fantastic 1920 brownstone building located at 2876 Hunboldt Ave.', 'South These apartments are beautiful and located in a very quiet and clean building.', 'Experience a clean quite building in uptown.', 'You will enjoy the many conveniences this neighborhood has to offer including  YWCA , Target , Lunds Grocery , Carabui  coffee shop  ,   restaurants, nearby shopping, multiple bus lines, and minutes away from both 35W and !', 'Heat, gas, water and trash are paid, and laundry is located on site for your convenience.', 'USI Fiber Optic Available - Cable-ready', 'ONE YEAR LEASE   NO PETS   NON SMOKING BUILDING    .', "If you have been imagining a classic styled apartment home then you'll like what you see!", "Of course, the easy access to all of Uptown's amenities and the lakes and even easier choice!", '   Did we mention that this apartment is spacious and bright!', '   Studio for $799.00', '1st Call', 'show contact info', 'FOR DETAILS AND SHOWINGS!', 'We no longer accept applications from smokers.', 'We do not work with subsidy progams.']
